Class Internship

Object
Internship
public class Internship extends Object
represent an internship posting created by a company representative stores available slots, timeline, level, majors, company and visibility state supports status change and slot confirmation logic

    Class

    Internship.Level
    represent internship year of study requirement BASIC: year 1â€“2 only INTERMEDIATE: suitable for year 3 and above students ADVANCED: suitable for year 3 and above students
    static enum 
    Internship.Status
    represent approval state PENDING: awaiting staff review APPROVED: visible for student application REJECTED: denied by staff FILLED: all available slots confirmed

      public Internship(String id, String title, String desc, Internship.Level level, String major, LocalDate startDate, LocalDate endDate, CompanyRepresentative cr, int slots, boolean isVisible, Company company)
      create new internship posting in pending state slot count automatically bounded between 1 and 10
      Parameters:
      id - internal internship id
      title - internship title
      desc - internship description
      level - academic level requirement
      major - preferred major
      startDate - application open date
      endDate - application close date
      cr - responsible company representative
      slots - requested max slot count
      isVisible - initial visibility flag
      company - offering company object
